OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome late
OL,6,Fsunny spells, then clear spells
OL,7,Fovernight, with showers, the showers
OL,8,Fbecoming less frequent and lighter.
OL,9,FNorthwesterly breeze continuing,
OL,10,Flocally strong in coastal parts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FSunny spells and showers,
OL,13,Fperhaps cloudier in west with more
OL,14,Fpersistent rain for a time. The
OL,15,Fshowers tending to die out through the
OL,16,Fafternoon. Breezy with winds turning
OL,17,Fmore northerly.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
