OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMainly
OL,6,Fdry with sunny spells Friday. Bright
OL,7,Fstart Saturday but becoming cloudy
OL,8,Fwith rain spreading east in afternoon.
OL,9,FRain clears overnight to leave sunny
OL,10,Fspells and a few showers Sunday.
